# --- Project Management (uv) ---
# Note: You SHOULD keep uv.lock in Git for applications. 
# Only ignore it if this were a shared library, but for an agent, keep it.
# .python-version is usually kept, but you can ignore it if you prefer 
# to let users decide their own Python version.

